data.clean_description: Carisoprodol is a prescription drug that is a centrally acting skeletal muscle relaxant that produces all the effects associated with barbiturates. It is a pro drug and is both structurally and pharmacologically related to tranquilizers which of course has a sedative effect on the user. This medication is extremely popular in the USA while it is not very common in Australia it is a great medication for muscle pain , anxiety and insomnia. Please check the Profile page for shipping cut off time as it is subject to change , Thank you.
